|Life study  ("Figure modelée d'après nature")
|Beaux-Arts de Paris, l'école nationale supérieure. Paris.
|align="center"|1895
|A work in plaster executed by Carli for the college and submitted for a competition for their "Grande Médaille".  The work is held by the college in their collection of the works of former pupils.
