|''"Dante aux enfers, le combat des démons"''
|Musée des Beaux-Arts de Marseille
|align="center"|1898
|This plaster [[bas-relief]] was shown at the 1898 Paris Salon and was purchased by the French State. It depicts [[Dante]] and [[Virgil]] watching two demons fighting.  In the exhibition catalogue it was entitled ''"Combat de démons"''. A fragment of the work is held by the Musée des Beaux-Arts de Marseille.
<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.culture.gouv.fr/public/mistral/caran_fr?ACTION=CHERCHER&FIELD_1=REF&VALUE_1=ARC00224
|title=Paris Salon 1898|accessdate=27 April 2014}}</ref>
<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.culture.gouv.fr/Wave/image/archim/0005/dafanch99_76650602_2.jpg
|title=Paris Salon 1898 2|accessdate=27 April 2014}}</ref>
