|"[[Omphale]]"
|Blois ; Musée du château de Blois
|align="center"|Date not known
|Terracotta figure acquired by the Blois museum in 1933.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.culture.gouv.fr/public/mistral/joconde_fr?ACTION=CHERCHER&FIELD_1=REF&VALUE_1=M0271011632
|title=Omphale|accessdate=2 May 2014}}</ref> This composition was subsequently executed in white marble
<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.artnet.com/artists/auguste-henri-carli/omphale-AcrGMTsl0C87iOaEQY1Ktw2
