|''"La Lutte de Jacob avec l'ange"''
|[[Clermont-Ferrand]].Place Michel de l'Hôpital
|align="center"|1902
|This marble work was also entitled ''"La Lutte de l'Esprit pour triompher de la Matière"'' .  Carli's  composition depicts a man fighting with an angel and the inscription reads {{Quotation|"ESPRIT ET LA MATIERE par CARLI"|}}

The working model in plaster was shown at the Paris Salon in 1902 and it was purchased for the Marseille Musée des Beaux-Arts. Carli made two maquettes of the work, one with the angel's wings spread and the second with wings folded.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vanderkrogt.net/statues/object.php?webpage=ST&record=frau032
|title=La Lutte de Jacob avec l'ange 1|accessdate=28 April 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://marseillesculptee.blogspot.co.uk/2008/06/latelier-muse-des-frres-carli-5.html
|title=La Lutte de Jacob avec l'ange 2|accessdate=28 April 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.culture.gouv.fr/public/mistral/joconde_fr?ACTION=RETROUVER&FIELD_98=REPR&VALUE_98=Jacob&NUMBER=13&GRP=0&REQ=%28%28Jacob%29%20%3aREPR%20%29&USRNAME=nobody&USRPWD=4%24%2534P&SPEC=3&SYN=1&IMLY=&MAX1=1&MAX2=1&MAX3=100&DOM=All 
|title=La Lutte de Jacob avec l'ange 3|accessdate=28 April 2014}}</ref>
